<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">用触摸板点击、拖动、滚屏操作</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">您可以直接在触摸板上进行单击、双击、拖动和滚动操作，而不需要切换到按键上。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p"><span class="link"><a href="touchscreen-gestures.html.zh-CN" title="使用触摸板和触摸屏手势">触摸板手势</a></span>会单独介绍。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<section id="secondary-click"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">副键点击</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">您可以自定义触摸板的副键点击（右键单击）操作。</p>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="list" style="list-style-type:bullet">
<li class="list"><p class="p">双指推动：用两根手指在任意位置推动。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">角落推动：用一根手指在角落处推动。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h3><span class="title">选择副键点击的方式</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击顶栏中的<span class="gui">触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在<span class="gui">点击</span>中，选择首选的点击方式。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="tap"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">轻触点击</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<div class="media media-image floatend"><div class="inner"><img src="figures/touch-tap.svg" class="media media-block" alt=""></div></div>
<p class="p">您可以轻点触摸板来代替使用鼠标进行点击。</p>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list">
<li class="list"><p class="p">要点击，在触摸板上触击。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">要双击，触击两次。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">要拖动一个项目，双击该项目但第二次点击后不要抬起手指。将物品拖动到想要的位置后抬起手指将其放下。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">如果您的触摸板支持多指点击，则可以通过两指同时点击来触发右键单击动作。否则您需要按下实体右键方可完成动作。请参阅<span class="link"><a href="a11y-right-click.html.zh-CN" title="模拟右键点击">模拟右键点击</a></span>获得更多关于模拟右键点击的信息。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">如果您的触摸板支持多指点击，三指同时点击可以模拟<span class="link"><a href="mouse-middleclick.html.zh-CN" title="单击中键">中键点击</a></span>动作。</p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">当用多指触击或拖动时，请确保您的手指分开足够的距离。如果手指太近，计算机可能会将其误认为单指操作。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h3><span class="title">启用轻触点击</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">触摸板</span>部分，确保<span class="gui">触摸板</span>开关为开启状态。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p"><span class="gui">触摸板</span>部分仅在您系统中包含触摸板的时候才可见。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换<span class="gui">轻触点击</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="twofingerscroll"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">双指滚动</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<div class="media media-image floatend"><div class="inner"><img src="figures/touch-scroll.svg" class="media media-block" alt=""></div></div>
<p class="p">您可以在触摸板上使用两根手指滚屏。</p>
<p class="p">选择此选项后，用单指轻触和拖动和平常操作一样，但如果您用两根手指在触摸板上拖动，则会自动滚动。在触摸板的顶部和底部之间移动手指可上下滚动，而在触摸板上横向移动手指可横向滚动。注意手指之间要有一定的间隔。如果手指靠得太近，触摸板可能将其识别为一根大的手指在操作。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">双指滚动可能在有些触摸板上无法工作。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h3><span class="title">启用双指滚动</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在<span class="gui">触摸板</span>部分，确保<span class="gui">触摸板</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换<span class="gui">双指滚动</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="edgescroll"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">边缘滚动</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<div class="media media-image floatend"><div class="inner"><img src="figures/touch-edge-scroll.svg" class="media media-block" alt=""></div></div>
<p class="p">如果您只想用一根手指滚动，请使用边缘滚动。</p>
<p class="p">您的触摸板的使用说明应该提供了用于边缘滚动的传感器的确切位置。通常，垂直滚动传感器位于触摸板的右侧。水平传感器位于触摸板的底部边缘。</p>
<p class="p">若要垂直滚动，请在触摸板的右边缘上下拖动手指。若要水平滚动，请在触摸板的底部边缘拖动手指。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">边缘滚动可能不适用于所有触摸板。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h3><span class="title">启用边缘滚动</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在<span class="gui">触摸板</span>部分，确保<span class="gui">触摸板</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换<span class="gui">边缘滚动</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="contentsticks"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">自然滚动</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">您可以使用触摸板拖动内容，像移动一张真正的纸一样。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">鼠标和触摸板</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在<span class="gui">触摸板</span>部分，确保<span class="gui">触摸板</span>开关已设为开启状态。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换<span class="gui">自然滚动</span>开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">此功能也被称为<span class="em">反向滚动</span>。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section class="links" role="navigation"><div class="inner">
